# PBMP Traceability Rule

Every commit, component, API, database table, service, and test must trace back to one or more of:

- Business Goal ID
- Requirement ID
- Use Case ID
- Acceptance Criteria ID
- NFR ID

## Code headers

```javascript
/**
 * PBMP Traceability
 * Requirement: REQ-SALES-001
 * Acceptance Criteria: AC-SALES-001, AC-SALES-002
 */
```

## API contracts

Add `x-pbmp-requirement-id` and `x-pbmp-acceptance-criteria` extensions to OpenAPI paths.

## Tests

Name describe/it blocks with Requirement and AC IDs.

If no traceability exists, do not implement the change.
